{"id":9310,"date":"2026-03-24T10:10:15","date_gmt":"2026-03-24T03:10:15","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=9310"},"modified":"2026-03-24T10:10:15","modified_gmt":"2026-03-24T03:10:15","slug":"webinar-khoa-hoc-tre-hoa-doc-quyen-cua-gsc","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/su-kien\/webinar-khoa-hoc-tre-hoa-doc-quyen-cua-gsc\/","title":{"rendered":"WEBINAR KHOA H\u1eccC \u0110\u1ed8C QUY\u1ec0N C\u1ee6A GSC: KH\u00c1M PH\u00c1 C\u00c1C PH\u01af\u01a0NG PH\u00c1P TR\u1eba HO\u00c1 TH\u1ebe H\u1ec6 M\u1edaI &amp; CHI\u1ebeN L\u01af\u1ee2C T\u00c1I T\u1ea0O SINH H\u1eccC T\u1ef0 TH\u00c2N"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1ee9 Ba, 31\/03\/2026 | 10:00 \u2013 11:30 | Online qua Zoom<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p tr\u1ebb ho\u00e1 da th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u2014 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t m\u00e0 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb t\u1ea7ng s\u00e2u nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac da? B\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt xu h\u01b0\u1edbng th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m 2026 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 v\u00e0 mang l\u1ea1i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng?<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>GSC \u2013 Global Shield Cosmetic<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng k\u00ednh m\u1eddi b\u1ea1n tham gia <\/span><b>Webinar Khoa H\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ed9c quy\u1ec1n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o <\/span><b>Th\u1ee9 Ba, ng\u00e0y 31\/03\/2026<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">, t\u1eeb 10:00 \u0111\u1ebfn 11:30, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn qua n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng Zoom.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ve-webinar-nay\"><\/span><b>V\u1ec0 WEBINAR N\u00c0Y<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 <\/span><b>&#8220;Skin-Booster T\u1eeb G\u1ed1c: C\u00e1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng Ph\u00e1p Tr\u1ebb Ho\u00e1 Th\u1ebf H\u1ec7 M\u1edbi &amp; Chi\u1ebfn L\u01b0\u1ee3c T\u00e1i T\u1ea1o Sinh H\u1ecdc T\u1ef1 Th\u00e2n&#8221;<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">, \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1ed9i th\u1ea3o chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u, n\u01a1i c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u chia s\u1ebb ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c y khoa c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt, ph\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb th\u1ef1c ti\u1ec5n v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng case l\u00e2m s\u00e0ng minh ch\u1ee9ng r\u00f5 n\u00e9t cho hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p tr\u1ebb ho\u00e1 t\u00e2n ti\u1ebfn nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Webinar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho <\/span><b>ch\u1ee7 spa, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt vi\u00ean da li\u1ec5u, chuy\u00ean vi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00fd c\u1ee7a GSC<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u2014 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch n\u00e2ng cao n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_9315\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-9315\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-9315 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/7.webp\" alt=\"Chuy\u00ean gia \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o trong webinar khoa h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a GSC\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/7.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/7-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/7-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/7-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-9315\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Chuy\u00ean gia \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o trong webinar khoa h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a GSC<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"noi-dung-chuong-trinh\"><\/span><b>N\u1ed8I DUNG CH\u01af\u01a0NG TR\u00ccNH<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 90 ph\u00fat \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia th\u00e0nh 3 ph\u1ea7n ch\u00ednh:<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"phan-1-cap-nhat-cac-phuong-phap-tre-hoa-the-he-moi-trinh-bay-boi-chuyen-gia-%e2%80%93-bac-si-thao\"><\/span><b>Ph\u1ea7n 1: C\u1eadp Nh\u1eadt C\u00e1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng Ph\u00e1p Tr\u1ebb Ho\u00e1 Th\u1ebf H\u1ec7 M\u1edbi<\/b> <i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">(Tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y b\u1edfi chuy\u00ean gia \u2013 B\u00e1c s\u0129 Th\u1ea3o)<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u webinar, di\u1ec5n gi\u1ea3 s\u1ebd ph\u00e1c ho\u1ea1 b\u1ee9c tranh to\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 <\/span><b>xu h\u01b0\u1edbng tr\u1ebb ho\u00e1 da n\u0103m 2026<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">, t\u1eeb c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 sinh h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ef1c tr\u1ea1ng nhu c\u1ea7u th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c spa v\u00e0 clinic hi\u1ec7n nay. C\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb ho\u00e1 ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u chi ti\u1ebft, c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng g\u1ee3i \u00fd th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf gi\u00fap ch\u1ee7 spa t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"phan-2-chien-luoc-tai-tao-sinh-hoc-tu-than-trinh-bay-boi-chuyen-gia-%e2%80%93-bac-si-ngoc\"><\/span><b>Ph\u1ea7n 2: Chi\u1ebfn L\u01b0\u1ee3c T\u00e1i T\u1ea1o Sinh H\u1ecdc T\u1ef1 Th\u00e2n<\/b> <i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">(Tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y b\u1edfi chuy\u00ean gia \u2013 B\u00e1c s\u0129 Ng\u1ecdc)<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a webinar, t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o th\u1ebf m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ed9c quy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a GSC. D\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u0129 H\u1ed3ng Ng\u1ecdc s\u1ebd tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a <\/span><b>B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i T\u1ebf B\u00e0o G\u1ed1c GSC<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u2014 g\u1ed3m <\/span><b>TBG Tr\u1ebb Ho\u00e1<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> v\u00e0 <\/span><b>TBG Ma Thu\u1eadt<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u2014 nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng trong ng\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb tr\u1ebb hoa v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, di\u1ec5n gi\u1ea3 s\u1ebd \u0111i s\u00e2u v\u00e0o <\/span><b>ph\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i &amp; t\u0103ng sinh Collagen t\u1ef1 th\u00e2n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Kem K (Recover Cream)<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u2013 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da sau \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>M\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i GSC<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u2013 b\u1ed5 sung d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Serum Advanced<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u2013 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c k\u00edch th\u00edch t\u0103ng sinh Collagen &amp; Elastin, t\u00e1i c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da t\u1eeb b\u00ean trong<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ed7i s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh case l\u00e2m s\u00e0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi nghe h\u00ecnh dung r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u00e1ch \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng trong th\u1ef1c ti\u1ec5n ngh\u1ec1 nghi\u1ec7p.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"phan-3-q-a-%e2%80%93-giai-dap-cung-chuyen-gia\"><\/span><b>Ph\u1ea7n 3: Q&amp;A \u2013 Gi\u1ea3i \u0110\u00e1p C\u00f9ng Chuy\u00ean Gia<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">K\u1ebft th\u00fac ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n h\u1ecfi \u2013 \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi c\u00e1c di\u1ec5n gi\u1ea3. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1eb7t nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n c\u00f2n \u0111ang b\u0103n kho\u0103n, th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c ca kh\u00f3 g\u1eb7p trong th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, ho\u1eb7c xin t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n v\u1ec1 ph\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1ec7p kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-9313 size-full\" style=\"font-size: 16px\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/5.webp\" alt=\"Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 90 ph\u00fat\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/5.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/5-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/5-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/03\/5-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><\/p>\n<p><strong>Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 90 ph\u00fat<\/strong><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tai-sao-ban-khong-nen-bo-lo\"><\/span><b>T\u1ea0I SAO B\u1ea0N KH\u00d4NG N\u00caN B\u1ece L\u1ee0?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 v\u00e0 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da \u0111ang thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t. Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y nay kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n da \u0111\u1eb9p h\u01a1n \u2014 h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n <\/span><b>k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 th\u1eadt, b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng v\u00e0 an to\u00e0n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m ngh\u1ec1 c\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Webinar c\u1ee7a GSC l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>N\u1eafm b\u1eaft xu h\u01b0\u1edbng tr\u1ebb ho\u00e1 2026<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00fang tr\u1edf n\u00ean ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>H\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb chuy\u00ean gia<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> qua c\u00e1c ca l\u00e2m s\u00e0ng c\u00f3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh minh ch\u1ee9ng c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>N\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p ph\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> t\u1ea1i c\u01a1 s\u1edf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng khoa h\u1ecdc<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>K\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng chuy\u00ean gia<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> trong h\u1ec7 sinh th\u00e1i GSC<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"-thong-tin-su-kien\"><\/span><b>\u00a0TH\u00d4NG TIN S\u1ef0 KI\u1ec6N<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><\/td>\n<td><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><b>Th\u1eddi gian<\/b><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1ee9 Ba, 31\/03\/2026 \u2013 10:00 \u0111\u1ebfn 11:30<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><b>H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c<\/b><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn qua Zoom<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><b>\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng<\/b><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ee7 spa, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt vi\u00ean da li\u1ec5u, chuy\u00ean vi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb, \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00fd GSC<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><b>Chi ph\u00ed<\/b><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u00e3y \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd ngay h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n! S\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi tham d\u1ef1 c\u00f3 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n \u2014 <\/span><b>GSC<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> mong \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng b\u1ea1n tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c khoa h\u1ecdc tr\u1ebb ho\u00e1 t\u1eeb g\u1ed1c.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%f0%9f%91%89-dang-ky-tham-gia-webinar\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\ud83d\udc49 <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/forms.gle\/v3M15YpB3Y6nhDfM6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><b>[\u0110\u0102NG K\u00dd THAM GIA WEBINAR]<\/b><\/a><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ecdi th\u1eafc m\u1eafc vui l\u00f2ng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 GSC \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3.<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>B\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p tr\u1ebb ho\u00e1 da th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u2014 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t m\u00e0 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb t\u1ea7ng s\u00e2u nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac da? B\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt xu h\u01b0\u1edbng th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 tr\u1ebb h\u00f3a, t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m 2026? Tham gia h\u1ed9i th\u1ea3o khoa h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ed9c quy\u1ec1n t\u1eeb GSC ngay.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":12,"featured_media":9314,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-9310","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-su-kien"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/9310","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/12"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=9310"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/9310\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":9317,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/9310\/revisions\/9317"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/9314"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=9310"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=9310"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":